{"tid":254425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【試題「辱華」】澳洲大學低頭惹爭議 當地人：要中國人教我哋點教書？","createTime":"2017-05-23T07:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T07:50:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"459de0ec56e686ebadf54b177bb5042937902498","tid":254425,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495522706_85fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495522706_85fe.jpg&h=d1a9a52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲名校考題稱中國官員喝醉時才說真話，掀起辱華風波，大學宣佈相關教授Aaron Wijeratne被停職，爭議試題已從學校網站撤下，正重審整個課程內容。事件引起澳洲網絡和民衆關注學術機構向華低頭自我審查之風，引起網絡熱議。<br />\n<br />\n蒙納殊大學(Monash University)人力資源管理課的一次小測試，試題刊登在該學校的網站上，面向包括中國人、印度人、澳洲人等在內的所有MG2340(課程代碼)的學生，但10道題有一半都與中國有關。如其中問題6：有俗語說，在中國，政府官員只有在＿＿＿＿的時候才會說真話：正確答案：d.當他們喝醉或者馬虎時。事後，除了當地 中國留學生不斷投訴，中國官方媒體發功炮轟辱華，澳洲中國使館發言人也承認墨爾本領館曾就事件與校方交涉，敦促調查。<br />\n<br />\n被停職的涉事教授表示不回應事件。事件引起澳洲網友熱議，炮轟學校向中國壓力低頭，有留言稱：「現在中國人要教我們如何教學了？這只是個開始。」<br />\n<br />\n《澳洲人報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56730997&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56730997%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=2JFlxaPkajhGzn5ZGSFtZDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=fcf68da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56730997%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=98330ca4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56730997&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a>"},{"pid":"d722a90c92f395c24e54fa29974f1a7175cce791","tid":254425,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"講真呢句留言好racist<br />\n有問題就有問題<br />\n無問題就無問題<br />\n邊個提出係無關係"},{"pid":"da9b8d27d5a8b52afb317a23fd072ffb6577d5fd","tid":254425,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"有邊個政府會講真話架"}]}